import Vue from 'vue'
import VueRouter from 'vue-router'
import Home from '../views/Home.vue'
import Login from'../views/LoginView.vue'
import { component } from 'vue/types/umd'

Vue.use(VueRouter)

const routes = [
  {
    path: '/',
    name: 'home',
    component: Home
  },


]

const router = new VueRouter({
  routes
})

export default router
